CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 3, 1946, pg. 27 reads: "Lovely Mermaids - Here are four of the ...ladies who will perform in Frogs' "Water Circus" next Friday night at Ammon Pool. Left to right; Yvonne Hall, Ann Drew, Christiania Muldrew and Jean Scott. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Yvonne Hall, Ann Drew, Christiania Muldrew and Jean Scott, posed on low diving board of Ammon recreation center swimming pool
